title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Experts say the U.S. baby formula shortage could continue throughout the rest of the year. Hyundai (OTCPK:HYMTF) is expected to announce a new  $7B electric vehicle plant in Georgia. Jerome Powell is expected to speak at a major conference, as he secures another four years as Federal Reserve Chairman.
